This should serve as a list of ideas and tips for groups who need to raise money for group functions.

==Fundraiser Ideas==
*Parties - Any kind of party - dinner, bowling, or anything else.  The social interaction strengthens ties between the individuals in the groups and it is a lot easier to ask someone to attend your fundraiser party than to just ask for money.
